<DocsLayout title="Reports" section="Dashboard & Reports">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Field Promax includes dozens of ready-made reports that provide valuable insights
    into your operations. These reports cover a wide range of aspects to help you analyze
    performance and make informed decisions.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our reports go beyond basic stats â€” they're designed for actionable insights.
    For example, the Scheduled vs. Actual Time Worked Analysis helps identify whether
    scheduling is off or if extra hours are being worked.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>From the left panel, select <strong>Reports</strong></li>
    <li>Choose a date range and parameters to generate reports</li>
    <li>All reports can be exported to Excel for further analysis</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Report Features</h2>
  <img src="/images/dashboard-reports/reports_01.png" alt="Reports Interface" />

  <h3>Quick Run</h3>
  <p>Generate any report by selecting the appropriate date range and parameters.</p>

  <h3>Favorites</h3>
  <p>Mark your most-used reports for quick access using the built-in favorites feature.</p>

  <h3>Export to Excel</h3>
  <p>Export any report to Excel for deeper analysis and custom reporting.</p>

  <h3>Custom Reports</h3>
  <p>View your custom reports in the Custom Reports tab.</p>

  <h2>Available Report Categories</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Work Order Reports:</strong> Open, closed, completed, by technician</li>
    <li><strong>Schedule Reports:</strong> Actual vs. scheduled time analysis</li>
    <li><strong>Estimate Reports:</strong> Pending, approved, conversion rates</li>
    <li><strong>Job Costing Reports:</strong> Profitability analysis by job</li>
    <li><strong>Timekeeping Reports:</strong> Hours worked by technician</li>
    <li><strong>Equipment Reports:</strong> Maintenance history, equipment by customer</li>
    <li><strong>Recurrence Reports:</strong> Future orders, generated orders</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only <strong>Administrators</strong> have access to Reports</li>
    <li>Reports reflect real-time data from your Field Promax account</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Export to Excel</strong> when you need additional filtering or advanced analysis.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Use favorites</strong> to quickly access reports you run regularly.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Contact support</strong> if you need custom reports specific to your business needs.
    </p>
  </div>
